"recommended since a default can be safely set in the event that the value is"
" not available in pillar and dictionaries can be traversed directly:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:57
msgid "Grains"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:59
msgid "The `grains` dictionary makes the minion's grains directly available:"
msgstr ""

