#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:73
msgid "env"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:75
msgid ""
"The `env` variable is available in sls files when gathering the sls from an "
"environment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:83
msgid "sls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/vars.rst:85
msgid ""
"The `sls` variable contains the sls reference value. The sls reference value"
" is the value used to include the sls in top files or via the include "
